{"id":290112,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/机智的县委书记：芦山脱表哥/","date":"2013-04-22T07:16:12Z","modified":"2014-10-21T20:00:30Z","title":"【麻辣总局】机智的县委书记：芦山脱表哥","content":"<p>陪李克强视察灾区的雅安芦山县县委书记范继跃这两天突然走红网络，被不少网民戏称为“机智的县委书记”、“脱表哥”等。这一切源于有细心的网民发现视察照片里的范继跃手腕处有明显的长期佩戴手表的印记，范很可能是为了避免重蹈“<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%E8%A1%A8%E5%93%A5%E8%A1%A8%E5%8F%94/\">表哥表叔</a>”们的覆辙而特意在陪同李克强出镜前摘下了手表。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/范继跃2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-290118\" alt=\"范继跃2\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/范继跃2.jpg\" width=\"352\" height=\"353\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/范继跃2.jpg 352w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/范继跃2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/范继跃2-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/范继跃2-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 352px) 100vw, 352px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/20130421210241323.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-290116\" alt=\"20130421210241323\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/20130421210241323.jpg\" width=\"615\" height=\"372\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/20130421210241323.jpg 615w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/20130421210241323-300x181.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/20130421210241323-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 615px) 100vw, 615px\" /></a></p>\n<p>以下为范继跃平时戴手表出镜的照片（图片来自网络）：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/139800463.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-290113\" alt=\"139800463\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/139800463.jpg\" width=\"540\" height=\"360\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/139800463.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chines